An '''abyssal leech''' is a [[Monsters|monster]] that dwells in the [[Abyss]], and also in the [[Abyssal Area]]. They are the easiest abyssal monsters to kill because they have low [[defence]], low [[strength]], and low [[hitpoints]]. However, they have a very high [[attack]] level and attack speed, attacking every second [[tick]], making them more dangerous than their combat level may suggest.

